{
  "texts": [
    "Formally we test for whether the panel time series is non-stationary using panel unit root tests.",
    "In particular we use Levin et al. (2002) (LLC) and Im et al. (2003) (IPS) Panel Unit Root tests.",
    "These methods applied to temperature changes confirm they are I(0) stationary.",
    "Both LLC and IPS have a null hypothesis of panel unit root.",
    "The results in Table A2 reject the null hypothesis for the panel time series temperature change (it) that the data is unit root, since the test statistic is much less than the critical value at the 1% statistical level."
  ]
}